      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Draft Bank Recovery and Resolution and Miscellaneous Provisions (Amendment) (EU Exit) Regulations 2018
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Draft statutory instrument, which will make amendments to UK legislation (including retained EU law) related to bank recovery and resolution, to be laid under the European Union (Withdrawal) Act 2018.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

